# Mesh:SetVertexMaterialWeight

This method sets the material weight of a single vertex in the mesh.

## Syntax

- **SetVertexMaterialWeight**(number vertex, number weight, number index)

| Parameter | Description |
|---|---|
| vertex | vertex index, starting with zero |
| weight | vertex texture coordinates to set, between zero and one |
| index | material index, can be 1, 2, 3, or 4 |
